This paper deals with natural language understanding and symbolic reasoning, which are core topics in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). It also involves the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and reinforcement learning (cs.LG) to optimize the performance of the system. Additionally, the paper falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with the development of intelligent systems that can perform complex tasks. Finally, the paper also involves software engineering (cs.SE) as it introduces a new system for semantic parsing.
